research_municipality_step.notes: Liberty City, TX operates under a Council/Manager form of government, which is categorized as mayor_council. All elected officials are elected at-large, so no specific divisions (wards, districts) are applicable. The terms for the Mayor and Mayor Pro Tem expire in May 2026, and for Council Members Bell, Dennis, and Dugger in May 2027, and for Council Members Seymour and Ward in May 2026.
